title: Human Events Daily - Sep 29 2021 -  Gen. Milley Calls Afghanistan Withdrawal a “Logistical Success”
description:
General Milley decides that the Afghanistan withdrawal a ‘logistical success’ and defends his decision not to resign, Chris Cuomo’s female executive producer begged to leave because they felt ‘threatened’ by him, this NBA star decides to pass on covid vaccine, and Psaki is asked to explain just how a $3.5T bill will be costless.


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
